#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:8
msgid "OptiImage"
msgstr "OptiImage"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:12
msgid "Image optimizer to reduce the size of images"
msgstr "Optimisator de imagine per reducer le grandor de imagines"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:19
msgid ""
"Optimize your images with OptiImage, a useful image compressor that supports "
"PNG, JPEG, WebP and SVG file types."
msgstr ""
"Optimisa tu images con OptiImage, un compressor utile de imagine que "
"supporta typos de file PNG, JPEG, WebP e SVG."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:21
msgid ""
"It supports both lossless and lossy compression modes with an option whether "
"to keep or not metadata of images. It additionally has a safe mode, where a "
"new image is created instead of overwriting the old one."
msgstr ""
"Il supporta sia modos de compression sin perdita que con perdita con un "
"option si mantener o non le metadatos de imagines. Additionalmente il ha un "
"modo secur, ubi un nove image es create in loco de super scriber ille vetere."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:24
msgid "It uses the following tools:"
msgstr "Il usa le sequente instrumentos:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:26
msgid "oxipng for PNG images"
msgstr "oxipng per imagines  PNG"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:27
msgid "jpegoptim for JPEG images"
msgstr "jpegoptim per images JPEG"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:28
msgid "scour for SVG images"
msgstr "scour per images SVG"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:29
msgid "cwebp for WebP images"
msgstr "cwebp per imagines  WebP"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:46
msgid "OptiImage main view showing a list of images getting processed"
msgstr ""
"Vista principal de OptiImage monstrante un lista de images que il va "
"processar"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.optiimage.metainfo.xml:53
msgid "Initial release of OptiImage"
msgstr "Version initial de OptilImage"
